reviewText: Not a concert, but a good documentary-type thing with plenty of Ellie, good DVD.

Don't waste your time or money, not deserving even a one star. Was ordered without prior reviews and consists of boring series of interviews with no performances. Was not sanctioned by Ellie and I believe it to be a rip off taking advantage of customers like myself that expected high quality as in all of her past CDs.
She's absolutely my favorite artist and this documentary, I'm sure, will be spot on! Pre-order immediately if your a fan!
